{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b47cb3c964","title":"大字报——党员的特权","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"39de4b52ef","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":17,"articleId":"b47cb3c964"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"80072ac412","name":"北京航空学院师生"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"26b998ad92","type":"title","text":"大字报——党员的特权","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b47cb3c964"},{"id":"e627b26438","type":"authors","text":"北京航空学院师生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b47cb3c964"},{"id":"2e678a58f8","type":"paragraph","text":"党员的特权分述如下：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b47cb3c964"},{"id":"b1627727f2","type":"paragraph","text":"一、迎接外宾，参加游园，理所当然是党员；","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b47cb3c964"},{"id":"89aeb918f8","type":"paragraph","text":"二、下厂实习，“一等厂”谁能去？","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b47cb3c964"},{"id":"169b0547fc","type":"paragraph","text":"三、毕业设计的分配“喷气式”谁能设计？","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b47cb3c964"},{"id":"24fb68ac7f","type":"paragraph","text":"四、党员有特权，来信也沾光，近水楼台先得月(例是裙带风)；","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b47cb3c964"},{"id":"afa1e45c02","type":"paragraph","text":"五、党员错误是认识，群众错误是立场，党员错误党内批评，群众错误公开批评；","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b47cb3c964"},{"id":"c4ff978f64","type":"paragraph","text":"六、我的都是对的，反对我就是反对党；","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b47cb3c964"},{"id":"2d0213360f","type":"paragraph","text":"七、赴苏留学谁选上，调学俄文搞“××”谁被调？","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b47cb3c964"},{"id":"27c1d0c56b","type":"paragraph","text":"八、你必须相信我，我可以不相信你等等，……","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b47cb3c964"},{"id":"675ba907b8","type":"paragraph","text":"小结：难怪有些同志带着“个人主义”、“特权思想”申请入党，难怪模范作用不知去向。铜墙铁壁就此筑成，党员特权谁赐与？原来是领导“恩赐”“党性”的表现。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b47cb3c964"},{"id":"afb0a47231","type":"paragraph","text":"参考资料：党章上是否有些规定？！","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b47cb3c964"},{"id":"7756f4247c","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：1957年5月18日新华通讯社编《内部参考》。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b47cb3c964"}],"page":{"id":"cd39cb9ab5","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b47cb3c964","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}